text: Russell William Fry (born January 31, 1985) is an American politician and lawyer. He has been the U.S. representative for South Carolina's 7th congressional district since 2023. He is a member of the Republican Party. Fry was a member of the South Carolina House of Representatives from 2015 to 2023. ==References== ==Other websites== * Congressman Russell Fry official U.S. House website * Russell Fry for Congress campaign website * Category:1985 births Category:Living people Category:United States representatives from South Carolina Category:Lawyers from South Carolina Category:Republican Party (United States) politicians
